Articles.Content:
So we at KAXA have just finished the development of a Munar Rover. There are three variants, Non-nuclear w/o parachute and Nuclear w/ parachute. With the parachute, we will be initially putting up a copy with stock parachutes, and then one with the RealChutes mod (It just makes it easier to land)

Edited December 9, 2013 by ethericalAlchemist
